Sentencas: A detailed numerical three-dimensional (3D) model for a planar solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) is developed in this paper.
Titulo: Transport, chemical and electrochemical processes in a planar solid oxide fuel cell: Detailed three-dimensional modeling

Sentencas: The 3D model takes into account detailed processes including transport, chemical and electrochemical processes taking place in the cell.
Titulo: Transport, chemical and electrochemical processes in a planar solid oxide fuel cell: Detailed three-dimensional modeling

Sentencas: Moreover, effects of the composite electrodes are taken into account by considering an electrochemically active layer of finite thickness in each of the electrodes.
Titulo: Transport, chemical and electrochemical processes in a planar solid oxide fuel cell: Detailed three-dimensional modeling

Sentencas: The developed model is applied to a repeating unit of an anode-supported SOFC working under direct internal reforming conditions.
Titulo: Transport, chemical and electrochemical processes in a planar solid oxide fuel cell: Detailed three-dimensional modeling

Sentencas: Detailed results for chemical species, temperature, current density and electric potential distribution are presented and discussed.
Titulo: Transport, chemical and electrochemical processes in a planar solid oxide fuel cell: Detailed three-dimensional modeling

Sentencas: It was found that the temperature distribution across the cell is more uniform in the interconnects than in the inner part of the cell.
Titulo: Transport, chemical and electrochemical processes in a planar solid oxide fuel cell: Detailed three-dimensional modeling

Sentencas: However, only small differences in the electric potential between the electrode and the corresponding interconnect are found.
Titulo: Transport, chemical and electrochemical processes in a planar solid oxide fuel cell: Detailed three-dimensional modeling

Sentencas: The current density in the electrodes is found to be high near the electrolyte and low deep into the electrochemically active layer.
Titulo: Transport, chemical and electrochemical processes in a planar solid oxide fuel cell: Detailed three-dimensional modeling

Sentencas: The current density is also low under the ribs of the interconnects.
Titulo: Transport, chemical and electrochemical processes in a planar solid oxide fuel cell: Detailed three-dimensional modeling
Transport, chemical and electrochemical processes in a planar solid oxide fuel cell: Detailed three-dimensional modeling
Transport, chemical and electrochemical processes in a planar solid oxide fuel cell: Detailed three-dimensional modeling
